{"type":"message","id":"1b7f2ea2","parentId":"0d16453f","timestamp":"2026-03-23T03:27:43.244Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The strategy_performance_panel_latest.json has a different structure than expected. Let me check the dashboard_portal_latest.html to see what's there. But more importantly, let me focus on what I've found so far:\n\n1. **Stale data issue (HIGH severity)**: The CSV index data is from 20260319, but today is 20260323. The halt decision this morning may have been based on outdated data. This is a significant concern.\n\n2. **Control tower**: All three accounts in RED/halt mode, no execution journal records.\n\n3. **No new buy orders executed** - as expected, the system is in HALT.\n   \n4. **Self-improvement ran successfully** - 20 high priority items still pending.\n\nSince the halt was triggered on stale data from 03-19, the current market conditions today could be materially different. This data freshness issue is serious enough that I should escalate it, especially given we're already in HALT mode and the day is progressing toward noon.","thinkingSignature":"96dda202e81a188b189b1cc11d899c10655fa692d4f7aa7cf139283f53c78524"},{"type":"text","text":"**11:26 心跳巡检结果**\n\n---\n\n**⚠️ 重要警报：CSV指数数据陈旧**\n\nscheduled_guard 报告（11:05）发现：\n\n> **CSV 指数数据陈旧（20260319 < 20260323）**\n> 严重级别：HIGH\n> 问题：早盘 halt 判断基于过时数据，今日实际市场状态未知\n\n这意味着今早 09:32 的 HALT 阻断决策，是用 03-19 的指数数据做出的，不是今日实时数据。今日（周一）开盘后的实际市场状态未经确认。\n\n---\n\n**当前各账户状态（控制塔 10:43）：**\n\n| 账户 | 状态 | 明日模式 | 累计收益 |\n|------|------|----------|----------|\n| 防御盘 | 🔴 RED | halt | -0.47% |\n| 平衡盘 | 🔴 RED | halt | -0.46% |\n| 进取盘 | 🔴 RED | halt | -0.39% |\n\n所有账户均无成交记录，执行日志为空。\n\n---\n\n**阻断原因已确认：**\n- 中证2000跌幅 -2.31%（基于 03-19 数据）\n- 市场宽度 9.2%（基于 03-19 数据）\n\n**但数据陈旧，实际今日跌幅可能已收窄或扩大，HALT 判断可靠性存疑。**\n\n---\n\n**建议关注：** 是否有实时数据源已恢复？若当前代理网络状态改善，可考虑重新运行一次盘中风控评估，确认是否维持 HALT 或可解除。\n\n其他子系统（策略审计、每日增强）无新增异常，Self-improvement 昨日执行完毕。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-